<br>
&quot;Yes, First let's plant the ginko. It's for mental alertness. Then, We'll plant the Siberian Ginseng, it's to improve mental energy and endurance. Good for patients looking for stress relief. But it can also calm the body.&quot;<br>
<br>
She takes out of the wheel barrell  a few pre-grown plants in their early stages. She laid a few down on the ground near where the hole was gong to be dug.<br>
<br>
&quot;OK, dig a nice hole just a bit bigger than the plant's soil base and place them gently into the hole place some water in and pack in gently the dirt.&quot; <p>-:¦:- Yakut -:¦:-<BR>
~Northern Amazon Shamaness~<BR>
